# NeoVision Layout System

## 容器

```css
.container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 32px;    /* 移动端 20px */
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;         /* 必须在光晕之上 */
}
```

## Bento Grid（首页核心布局）

```css
.bento {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  grid-auto-rows: 180px;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 100px;
}
```

卡片通过 span 控制尺寸（见组件规则），不固定宽高。

## News Grid

```css
.news-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
}
```

## Section 间距

| 区域 | 值 |
|------|-----|
| Hero padding | `100px 0 80px` |
| Bento → News | `margin-bottom: 100px` |
| Section-head → 内容 | `margin-bottom: 48px` |
| Section-head eyebrow → h2 | `margin-bottom: 8px` |

## Section Head 通用样式

```css
.section-head .eyebrow {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 550;
  letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-3);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.section-head h2 {
  font-size: 28px; font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: -0.6px;
  color: var(--text);
}
```

## Hero 区域

```css
.hero { padding: 100px 0 80px; text-align: center; }
.hero-label {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 550;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -2px;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero h1 strong { font-weight: 600; }
.hero p {
  font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-2);
  max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto;
  font-weight: 380; letter-spacing: -0.2px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}
```

## 响应式断点

| 断点 | 条件 | Bento 列 | News 列 | 其他 |
|------|------|----------|---------|------|
| Desktop | >900px | 4 列 | 3 列 | nav links 显示 |
| Tablet | ≤900px | 2 列 | 2 列 | 隐藏 nav-links，Hero 缩小 |
| Mobile | ≤560px | 1 列 | 1 列 | padding 20px，card 22px，Bento auto-rows |

**Tablet (≤900px)：**
```css
.bento { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); grid-auto-rows: 160px; gap: 12px; }
.news-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
.hero { padding: 64px 0 56px; }
.nav-links { display: none; }
```

**Mobile (≤560px)：**
```css
.container, .nav-inner { padding: 0 20px; }
.bento { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-auto-rows: auto; gap: 10px; }
.card-2x2, .card-2x1, .card-1x2, .card-1x1 {
  grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; min-height: 160px;
}
.card-2x2 { min-height: 280px; }
.card-1x2 { min-height: 220px; }
.news-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; }
.footer-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
.footer-links { gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
```

## CSS 书写顺序

每个规则块内属性按此顺序排列：
1. **定位** — position, top, right, bottom, left, z-index
2. **盒模型** — display, width, height, padding, margin, border, border-radius
3. **排版** — font-family, font-size, font-weight, letter-spacing, line-height, text-align, text-transform, color
4. **视觉** — background, backdrop-filter, filter, opacity, box-shadow
5. **动效** — transition, animation, cursor, pointer-events

## class 命名规范

- 全 kebab-case：`.card-title` `.news-excerpt` `.footer-links`
- 尺寸修饰用 `-NxN` 后缀：`.card-2x2` `.card-1x2`（不叫 `.card-large`）
- 颜色变体用叠加 class：`.card-tag.warm`（不叫 `.card-tag-warm`）
- CSS 分区注释：`/* ── Section Name ── */`
